. algorithm
.. pragma tracking
-> during the pragma pass, xkaapi {task,data} pragmas are
registered along with their location

.. function tracking
-> every entered function is tracked if a corresponding
pragma is found. the lookup is done by (file, line)

.. call code modification

.. variable assigment modification
